      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>into wedges, then separate the wedges into 'petals'</p><p>Cut the <strong>chicken breast portions </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p>",
