    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped chicken</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for an initial 3-4 min or until lightly browned</p><p>Once lightly browned, add the <strong>onion petals </strong>and cook for a further 5-6 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the onion has softened</p>",
